      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in superlative condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, it exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that retains its original showroom luster. Mechanically beyond reproach, this specimen offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
