    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You are looking at an absolute dream of a car! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of this beauty\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There isn't a single blemish on it, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car smell! It\u2019s been tucked away safely in my garage and driven very sparingly. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm looking for someone who will appreciate a ride that's in truly flawless shape. You've gotta see this one in person to believe it! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
