    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. This specimen features the legendary 13B-REW power plant, maintaining exceptional compression across all rotor faces. The sequential twin-turbocharger system executes a seamless transition at 4,500 RPM, delivering linear boost pressure without hesitation. The chassis remains incredibly rigid, supported by a factory-spec four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution. Every vacuum line has been meticulously inspected, and the five-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement. Finished in its original pigment with a preserved interior, this FD represents a rare opportunity to own a pure, unmolested example of the '90s JDM golden era.",
